{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea59c82b67","title":"中学教师的右派言论（五）","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a31026fa4d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"ea59c82b67"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0c1b5e3467","name":"朱辛孟"},{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"418723fea3","name":"张雨田"},{"id":"8c843b464c","name":"孙振漠"},{"id":"ac1fff2ffa","name":"杨维汉"},{"id":"bbcb982693","name":"乔占魁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1e9c9c9836","type":"title","text":"中学教师的右派言论（五）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"737cf2dc99","type":"authors","text":"山西杨维汉孙振漠朱辛孟乔占魁张雨田","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"2980eb804e","type":"paragraph","text":"杨维汉（太原四中教师）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"c18cf155ed","type":"paragraph","text":"“当今教条主义满天飞，对青年灌输毒素，使得人没有了灵魂，只会随声附和，没有自己主张”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"602ff56805","type":"paragraph","text":"“解放后对非党人士不信任，用人不是看能不能、贤不贤、而看员不员，不是党员的有能力也不能提升，而那些没有能力的、挂名的却提升了”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"a2f3d98dde","type":"paragraph","text":"孙振漠（运城中学教师）：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"68a949a10b","type":"paragraph","text":"“民盟必须象共产党一样，在全国各地、各部门和各基层组织发展，否则就不能和共产党平起平坐，就不能相互监督；必须在青年中发展组织，否则便不能长期共存”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"23405a6258","type":"paragraph","text":"朱辛孟（太原第六中学教师）：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"812f2fa434","type":"paragraph","text":"“民盟在学校中的工作，只是党的附属机构，在工作上不敢大胆工作，客观上有压力，因为是受党的领导，只形成是‘备员充数’，党布置一些重要工作也不早告诉，盟也不能有所准备，好像不是一个平等对待，所以在参加一些会议上是有精神刺激的”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"d087b236f2","type":"paragraph","text":"“关于‘长期共存，互相监督’，是一个长期的方针，但我个人觉得很渺茫”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"075579e9e6","type":"paragraph","text":"乔占魁（晋城一中教师）：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"69bd4fd0fe","type":"paragraph","text":"“统购统销本身是不好的，党不得已而用之”。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"09a58666cf","type":"paragraph","text":"张雨田（高平一中教师）：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"},{"id":"3496dce067","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党不是用人唯贤，而是用人唯亲。领导上除信任党团员之外，还信任积极分子，信任那些溜、舔、奉、承、敬的人，拉老亲戚，把这些人看成是积极分子”。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67"}],"page":{"id":"b6e99f6b9e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ea59c82b67","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}